title: Upstairs bdrm in quiet house, all util incl, across from UWRF
map_address: 615 Oak Knoll Ave near Cascade Ave
posting_body: ['Second-floor bedroom in a house on Cascade Ave.', '(blue house with white trim) across from UWRF campus.', 'The currently available bedroom is roughly 9.5 ft x 11.5 ft with shelving, counter, and small clothing rod/closet.', 'Most bedrooms themselves are not furnished (but if you would like an item feel free to ask if I have something available).', 'The main floor living room, dining room, and kitchen (full-size refrigerator, stovetop/oven, microwave, dishwasher, toaster, teapot, etc.) are partially furnished since owner lives in house, too.', 'The house has two full bathrooms, one on second floor and another on the main floor (primarily for main floor bedroom).', 'All utilities are included (internet, gas, electric, trash, water) and full laundry is available in the basement rec.', 'room (washer and dryer, free).', 'Detached two-car garage in back.', 'Additional off-street parking space is available in the back of the house for all vehicles.', 'Owner is faculty member at UWRF (astro/physics).']
